## 17. Recomendaciones DevOps

### Entornos

```
development → staging → production
    │             │          │
    ▼             ▼          ▼
  Local      Vercel       Vercel
  MongoDB    Preview      Production
  Local      Atlas Dev    Atlas Prod
```

### CI/CD Pipeline (GitHub Actions)

```yaml
# .github/workflows/ci.yml (conceptual)
on: [push, pull_request]
jobs:
  lint-and-test:
    - Checkout
    - Setup Node 20
    - Install dependencies
    - Run ESLint + Prettier
    - Run unit tests (Jest/Vitest)
    - Run integration tests
  
  deploy-preview:  # Solo en PR
    - Deploy a Vercel Preview
    - Run E2E tests (Cypress/Playwright)
  
  deploy-production:  # Solo en main
    - Deploy a Vercel Production
    - Smoke tests
    - Notificar al equipo
```

### Herramientas Recomendadas

| Categoría | Herramienta | Propósito |
|-----------|------------|----------|
| Linting | ESLint + Prettier | Consistencia de código |
| Testing | Vitest + React Testing Library | Unit/Integration |
| E2E | Playwright | Tests end-to-end |
| Commits | Commitlint + Husky | Conventional commits |
| Versionado | Semantic Release | Versionado automático |
| Monitoreo | Sentry | Error tracking |
| Logs | Pino / Winston | Logging estructurado |
| Docs API | Swagger/OpenAPI | Documentación de API |

